    "category": "holy_spirit",
    "question_zh": "圣灵在基督徒生命中做什么工作？",
    "question_en": "What does the Holy Spirit do in a Christian's life?",
    "short_answer_zh": "圣灵使人重生、赐人信心、内住在信徒里面、使人成圣、赐下属灵恩赐、引导信徒明白真理、为信徒代求，并作为我们将来得基业的凭据。",
    "short_answer_en": "The Holy Spirit regenerates, gives faith, indwells believers, sanctifies, gives spiritual gifts, guides into truth, intercedes for believers, and serves as the guarantee of our future inheritance.",
    "detailed_answer_zh": "圣灵在基督徒生命中的工作可以从几个方面理解：\n\n首先是重生和归信。人靠自己无法相信福音（林前2:14），是圣灵使死在罪中的人活过来（弗2:1-5），赐给他们新心（结36:26-27），使他们能够悔改和相信。\n\n其次是成圣。重生是一次性的，但成圣是一生的过程。圣灵在信徒里面持续工作，使他们越来越像基督（林后3:18），结出圣灵的果子——仁爱、喜乐、和平、忍耐、恩慈、良善、信实、温柔、节制（加5:22-23）。\n\n第三是恩赐和事奉。圣灵按照自己的旨意赐给每位信徒不同的属灵恩赐（林前12:4-11），目的是建造基督的身体——教会。没有任何恩赐是不重要的，也没有任何信徒是没有恩赐的。\n\n最后，圣灵是我们得基业的凭据（弗1:13-14），就像定金一样，保证上帝会完成祂在我们身上开始的善工。",
    "detailed_answer_en": "The Holy Spirit's work in a Christian's life can be understood in several aspects:\n\nFirst, regeneration and conversion. People cannot believe the gospel on their own (1 Cor 2:14); it is the Spirit who makes those dead in sin alive (Eph 2:1-5), gives them a new heart (Ezek 36:26-27), and enables repentance and faith.\n\nSecond, sanctification. Regeneration is a one-time event, but sanctification is a lifelong process. The Spirit works continually within believers, making them increasingly Christlike (2 Cor 3:18), producing the fruit of the Spirit — love, joy, peace, patience, kindness, goodness, faithfulness, gentleness, self-control (Gal 5:22-23).\n\nThird, gifts and ministry. The Spirit gives each believer different spiritual gifts according to His will (1 Cor 12:4-11), for building up Christ's body — the church. No gift is unimportant, and no believer is without gifts.\n\nFinally, the Spirit is the guarantee of our inheritance (Eph 1:13-14), like a down payment, assuring us that God will complete the good work He began in us.",
