    "id": "q107",
    "category": "sin_and_salvation",
    "question_zh": "怎样才可以得救？",
    "question_en": "How can I be saved?",
    "short_answer_zh": "承认自己是罪人，相信耶稣基督为你的罪死而复活，接受祂为你的救主和生命的主——这就是得救的路。",
    "short_answer_en": "Acknowledge that you are a sinner, believe that Jesus Christ died and rose for your sins, and receive Him as your Savior and Lord — this is the way of salvation.",
    "detailed_answer_zh": "得救的方法，圣经说得非常清楚：\n\n**第一步：认识自己的处境。**「世人都犯了罪，亏缺了神的荣耀」（罗马书3:23）。每个人在神面前都是罪人，无法靠自己的努力达到神的标准。\n\n**第二步：相信基督的救赎。**「神爱世人，甚至将他的独生子赐给他们，叫一切信他的不至灭亡，反得永生」（约翰福音3:16）。耶稣在十字架上代替我们承受了罪的刑罚，第三天复活，胜过了死亡。\n\n**第三步：用信心回应。**「你若口里认耶稣为主，心里信神叫他从死里复活，就必得救」（罗马书10:9）。这不是仅仅知道关于耶稣的事实，而是全心信靠祂。\n\n**需要强调的是：**\n- 得救完全是靠恩典，不是靠行为（以弗所书2:8-9）\n- 得救不需要先把自己变好——你是在罪中被神拯救的\n- 得救是即时的，但成圣（生命改变）是一生的过程\n- 得救后当加入教会，接受装备和牧养\n\n你现在就可以向神祷告：「主耶稣，我承认我是罪人，无法自救。我相信你为我的罪死在十字架上，又从死里复活。我愿意接受你做我的救主和主。求你进入我的生命，赦免我的罪，赐我新生命。阿们。」",
    "detailed_answer_en": "The way of salvation is stated very clearly in Scripture:\n\n**Step 1: Recognize your condition.** 'All have sinned and fall short of the glory of God' (Romans 3:23). Everyone stands as a sinner before God, unable to meet His standard through their own effort.\n\n**Step 2: Believe in Christ's redemption.** 'For God so loved the world, that he gave his only Son, that whoever believes in him should not perish but have eternal life' (John 3:16). Jesus bore the punishment for our sins on the cross and rose on the third day, conquering death.\n\n**Step 3: Respond in faith.** 'If you confess with your mouth that Jesus is Lord and believe in your heart that God raised him from the dead, you will be saved' (Romans 10:9). This isn't merely knowing facts about Jesus but wholehearted trust in Him.\n\n**Key points:**\n- Salvation is entirely by grace, not by works (Ephesians 2:8-9)\n- You don't need to fix yourself first — God saves you while you're still in sin\n- Salvation is immediate, but sanctification (life transformation) is a lifelong process\n- After salvation, join a church for discipleship and spiritual nurture\n\nYou can pray right now: 'Lord Jesus, I confess that I am a sinner and cannot save myself. I believe You died on the cross for my sins and rose from the dead. I receive You as my Savior and Lord. Enter my life, forgive my sins, and give me new life. Amen.'",
    "bible_verses": [
      "Romans 3:23",
      "John 3:16",
      "Romans 10:9",
